    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, featuring the iconic 996.2 widebody architecture and a meticulously maintained 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six powerplant. This specimen features a documented LN Engineering IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced rear main seal, ensuring mechanical longevity. The Getrag G96/01 six-speed manual transmission provides precise, tactile gear selection, sending power to all four wheels through a viscous-coupling AWD system. The suspension geometry remains factory-perfect, utilizing original Bilstein dampers and upgraded GT3-spec control arm bushings for sharpened turn-in. Finished in Arctic Silver Metallic with zero paint depth variance, the exterior is paired with a flawless black full-leather interior showing no bolster compression. Riding on 18-inch hollow-spoke 'Turbo Look' wheels with fresh N-rated Michelin rubber, this C4S is a turn-key analog masterpiece for the serious driver.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
